   <text>
      <body>
        <div>
            <pb facs="#TL-0435.jpg" n="part3_p043.jpg" xml:id="img_0043" corresp="https://id.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/tillich-lectures/part3_p043.jpg"/>
            
            <p facs="#facs_43_tr_3">
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_3_tl_1" n="N001"/>e
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>-430-
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>treatment, and the automomous ideal of creative out of human freedom, and following the
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>rational structure of thought and the aesthetic structure and the esthical structure; and on the
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_3_tl_5" n="N005"/>other hand the religious.traditions, which were partly very much OUTSIDE this situation.
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_3_tl_6" n="N006"/>And to this moment, today, I believe there is only one possibility, namely a possibility
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_43_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>which I will call (and ask for your permission) by the old, beautiful and (as [with] all these words)
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>deteriorized name: initiation—from the Latin, "going-into" something, namely into what?: into the
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>mysteries, in the mystery cults, into the esoteric inner knowledge. I take this as a metaphor.
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>I don’t want to establish a new mystery religion, with this /some daughter] —for this you better
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>go to Iifornia! [laughter] —but what I want to say is that beyond the humanisticòvelopment of
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>man’s potentialities, beyond the public education to Neills and beyond theefroduction into the
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/> religious groups and their symbols and rite, there is something higher than all of them, namely
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>the mysterious of life itself, the answer to the question of the meaning of our existence. And
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>initiation would mean: to show in all these three forms of education the point in which they
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>cease to be sufficient--and that's what Protestantism can do, even with itself as [an example] :
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_43_tr_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>it can and must show its own insufficiency. There is in the mystery of life something which
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_2" n="N002"/>transcends the Christian answer, if the Christian answer is taken in terms of church doctrine and
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_3" n="N003"/>church rituals and church morale. This ultimate transcends every concrete situation, but expenses
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_4" n="N004"/>itself secularly as well as religiously in the symbol ofEieularism as weil as in the Abbols of
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_5" n="N005"/>religion, but is not bound to any of them...
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_6" n="N006"/>So I would say: in education it success not only to use the humanistic counterbalance
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_7" n="N007"/>Cela nʼentraîne de lʼauteur beaucoup de nouveau.
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_8" n="N008"/>Mais elle est vrai le
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_9" n="N009"/>dire une
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_10" n="N010"/>Monsieur
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_11" n="N011"/>dʼacquerir
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_12" n="N012"/>dans le
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_13" n="N013"/>dʼune manière est devenu
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_14" n="N014"/>dʼun autre
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_15" n="N015"/>Je ne suis
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_16" n="N016"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_17" n="N017"/>dʼOndine
               <lb facs="#facs_43_tr_2_tl_18" n="N018"/>dʼun autre
            </p>
            
